{"tid":1842363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟留低藍絲反對醫護罷工論，我秒回解答你","createTime":"2020-01-25T15:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T16:14:42.000Z","uid":330057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5464446ee56607a024a2730c2b1b9040d81443ec","tid":1842363,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n罷工嘅話啲病人點？<br />\n<br />\n1. 緊急服務係會維持，但非緊急服務就只能有限度維持。<br />\n但同時間你諗下，如果香港發生大量社區疫症爆發，非緊急服務都係要減少（沙士就係咁）而且一旦爆發對社會嘅損失係更加大（公共交通工具，大中小學校園，公園，公司，，你同我都有染病生命危險。而且你覺得係呢一屆政府承擔得起嘅責任咩？發生人命佢點賠？沙士死咗幾多醫生護士係咪唔記得？<br />\n而且上前線嘅醫護人員佢哋都有自己嘅家庭同生活，點解就唔可以減低呢個風險，令到全香港人唔使冒咁大嘅險？"},{"pid":"e860fe93f8e0d53d60f904d11c19d6224314a1bb","tid":1842363,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"我睇唔到我唔知，你唔做就係你失職"},{"pid":"1e322f946a9236e2263d1bfb1d5dfb5e137f7214","tid":1842363,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703607b75d5916aa5a64ad0b8ba01b0b6e9d92bc","tid":1842363,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"封關會令到經濟造成重大損失<br />\n<br />\n1. 但如果因為冇封關而引發社區爆發，咁損失一定會嚴重過封關。<br />\n你諗下而家最多係冇咗中國遊客<br />\n但係本地人依然會出嚟買嘢消費<br />\n但如果出現社區爆發，人心惶惶，香港人一定會減少出街消費嘅意欲同次數<br />\n咁樣嘅話對經濟造成嘅損失係更加大"},{"pid":"c1b252eeef6dc1149b5e1a06f6c218a7072f726c","tid":1842363,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:55:50.000Z","msg":"覺得有意思嘅求下你哋幫手push<br />\n真係有用嘅話搵人幫我整合成為文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81d39231ca94be7f6c34a902b19b25b529c5ffc","tid":1842363,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e860fe93f8e0d53d60f904d11c19d6224314a1bb","tid":1842363,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"我睇唔到我唔知，你唔做就係你失職"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"政府唔做就一定係佢失職<br />\n但你認為佢承擔得起呢啲責任咩？<br />\n假設佢失左職之後啦？<br />\n到時香港經濟已經重創，日常生活受到嚴重影響<br />\n咁點解唔早啲做有效嘅措施？"},{"pid":"7506c8309559939d4d0a3f027c44512da63c9795","tid":1842363,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:58:49.000Z","msg":"係咪真係多字就唔睇？<br />\n定係大家淨係想睇中國仆街嗰啲文章？"},{"pid":"bb981bd40b285e874214b954fc0b50c47f450528","tid":1842363,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:00:53.000Z","msg":"心淡"},{"pid":"961537d55cba47879295e0a37bb3828d5bf029e8","tid":1842363,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e322f946a9236e2263d1bfb1d5dfb5e137f7214","tid":1842363,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:01:16.000Z","msg":"幫我push pls"},{"pid":"f5c2ef7321d3c6242333f0d88d65b3790f672015","tid":1842363,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:01:23.000Z","msg":"因為藍絲都屌緊政府點解唔封，我親戚都屌緊政府慢吞吞畀高鐵一車車入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30281ee6a1b7c6ce91847bc0ffd09c28022a32c","tid":1842363,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5c2ef7321d3c6242333f0d88d65b3790f672015","tid":1842363,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:01:23.000Z","msg":"因為藍絲都屌緊政府點解唔封，我親戚都屌緊政府慢吞吞畀高鐵一車車入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:02:07.000Z","msg":"我身邊啲垃圾親戚唔係咁喎<br />\n仲喺度話搞亂香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e80f4ac518e70204860fab28155b9